node.text:
Because of you I’ve learned about true friendship, you forgive me when I’m wrong but never lose respect for me. The way you speak to me has taught about patience; about even self-worth. Not every person with a huge following influences, she’s the biggest influence on us; on me, on all of us. You help me stay grounded to the reality of our lives, you are RICH in your soul, you’ve been rich, I’m just happy I get to grow with you. You are the definition of HIGH MAINTENANCE..

I celebrate you every day, every day! Today is no different and this weekend is UP!!!!!

node.text:
Touch my soul gently because nobody can🌊 . Growing up, growing strong, growing within , growing together … just growing. Nobody said it was going to be easy, it’s painful. Listen to the ocean roar, ignore the outside noise and keep going . Wipe your tears and keep your head straight because it’s only one way. 
When a Queen cries, the world feels it. Exude power, exude love, exude passion but NEVER lose yourself.
